summary:
Complete reverse engineering analysis of TransVideoAI v4.1 showing:
1. Activation form is a dummy - always returns 'invalid' regardless of input
2. gfx.exe is malware that installs backdoor/miner (Microsoft Edge Update disguise)
3. Malware persistence via Windows Defender exclusions, scheduled tasks, and services
4. Real app is Python-based with AI/video processing capabilities
